metadata.name: Wu Tiger #1
metadata.description:
From the slums of Shaolin comes Wu Tiger Clan, a new and exclusive "Members Only" community. It combines all-things music, philosophy, gaming, tech, entertainment, and movies to create a forever culture!

As word is bond, utility is top priority but it doesn't mean it has to be boring. Stay fresh with the Wu-Tiger Clan while reaping the benefits of being part of a forward thinking, web3 based, solutions-oriented family.
